  "title": "Introduction to Algorithms in Java",
  "lessonText": "This lesson introduces the fundamental concepts of algorithms in Java.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Algorithms are step-by-step procedures for solving problems.\n- They can be implemented using various data structures.\n- Understanding algorithms is crucial for writing efficient code.\n- Java provides built-in libraries for common algorithms.\n- Analyzing algorithm efficiency helps in optimizing performance."
